My first ever @LEGO stop-motion! For their #RebuildTheWorld campaign, which is all about exploring the unlimited creative possibilities with LEGO, I challenged myself to animate transitions between LEGO models. I built and rebuilt with LEGO bricks countless times during this process to see how far I could push my creativity and imagine something different coming to life from an already existing build. So how do you smoothly animate from one model to another? Well, you have to get creative and build custom in-between frames - swipe to see some of my favorite frames! #RebuiltByKevin #Sponsored
